s/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係 你話屋企仲有藥所以唔諗住出去睇 睇一次醫生都幾百 差唔多成日人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f08b782f89d86c98d99b1384e56d8f5e1d890e2","tid":23352,"uid":22116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"首先查清楚你係咪假自僱先<br />\n假如固定時間固定地點只為同一個人提供服務，有可能係假自僱，張自僱約可以無效<br />\n依點好睇法律條文字眼，自己打去勞工處問<br />\n第二，如果你係自僱，咁你同佢既關係就係服務供求關係，睇清楚同佢簽過既約有冇列明提供服務規律，同埋無法提供服務既通知期，如果冇既話緊係唔洗理佢<br />\n佢問你拎假紙，你直情可以錄佢音告佢視你為僱員但冇幫你買勞保<br />\n<br />\n利申唔太熟勞工條例，打上去勞工處問啦，佢D人真係答到你問題，唔係hea鳩你"},{"pid":"652c99ef83c6fa61b3bbe15f4cbbbf37092cc450","tid":23352,"uid":18596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>39.2度你都要去睇醫生架啦<br />\n<br />\n不過見佢咁柒串緊係唔撚比</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我留左係屋企食藥瞓教 唔諗住睇 太貴啦睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係 你話屋企仲有藥所以唔諗住出去睇 睇一次醫生都幾百 差唔多成日人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照講冇睇醫生，我相信佢唔敢炒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7802c4455303de83453bc624588b71fbeedaa2f7","tid":23352,"uid":15754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:31:49.000Z","msg":"On9不嬲話射就射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫生紙用黎claim 學校attendance"},{"pid":"65df63e37ae9c0facd8d9bad95111f9d5edf6ae0","tid":23352,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自僱人仕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你請班裝修佬黎你屋企裝修，裝修佬病左，使唔使比醫生紙你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢仲要係前排先叫我簽 愈諗條氣愈唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm